title: BREAKING: Girl fighting for life after Storm Doris winds collapse school roof on class
text: BREAKING: Girl fighting for life after Storm Doris winds collapse school roof on class BREAKING: Girl fighting for life after Storm Doris winds collapse school roof on class A SCHOOLGIRL has been rushed to hospital with life threatening injuries after raging Storm Doris winds caused the roof of a school hall to collapse on to a class of children.
